<h2 class="text-center">Petition</h2>

<div class="petition-text">
  <p class="lead">
    <i class="fa fa-quote-left" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Israeli-Palestinian conflict is responsible for horrendous misery and suffering on both sides.
  </p>
  <p class="lead">
    We call on our governments to renew their efforts to foster the conditions necessary for a resolution to the conflict.
  </p>
  <p class="lead">
    We call on the Palestinian leadership to recognise Israel's right to a peaceful existence and to commit to non-violence.
  </p>
  <p class="lead">
    We call on the Israeli government to commit to the creation of a Palestinian state and to end settlement building in the occupied territories. <i class="fa fa-quote-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="text-center alert alert-warning" role="alert"">
  <span id="counter">Counter text</span> signatures
</div>

<div class="container sign-petition text-center">
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning">Sign this petition</button>
</div>

<%= render 'share_petition' %>
